ActSpecies at Risk Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the Species at Risk Act
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE 1 to the SPECIES AT RISK ACT in order to add 7 aquatic species to the Schedule, reclassify 2 species and strike out 1 species previously listed and adding 2 new designatable units of the same species in its place. One designatable unit of a terrestrial species, currently also listed as part of a broader designatable unit, is struck out to eliminate duplication.
